<subSubSection id="B9B6650D970BE363F1F4FBDC0797023F" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="F1133686970BE363F1F4FBDC0797023F" blockId="8.[151,1437,1095,1301]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F1F4FBDC0745034A" bold="true" box="[151,267,1095,1120]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="36AC4D05970BE363F077FBD30400034A" authorityName="Pinheiro &amp; Araujo Junior" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="Pinheiro &amp; Araujo Junior" baseAuthorityYear="2017" box="[276,590,1096,1120]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Episcepsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coeruleocephala" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F077FBD30400034A" box="[276,590,1096,1120]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">Episcepsis coeruleocephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="D8EB57EF970BE363F334FBDC0494034A" box="[599,730,1095,1120]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F334FBDC0494034A" bold="true" box="[599,730,1095,1120]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">comb. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
was described from an undetermined number of males. Only one was found at the 
<collectionCode id="97BDAE43970BE363F0E0FBF6079503AE" box="[387,475,1133,1156]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">BMNH</collectionCode>
. To our knowledge, this species is known only from the 
<typeStatus id="2E178824970BE363F52FFBF702F803AF" box="[1100,1206,1132,1157]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">lectotype</typeStatus>
, which is why it was not possible to dissect it. The closest described species is 
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F220FB0A059A0382" box="[835,980,1168,1192]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">
<taxonomicName id="36AC4D05970BE363F220FB0A059E0382" baseAuthorityName="Druce" baseAuthorityYear="1897" box="[835,976,1168,1192]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Episcepsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moloneyi">E. moloneyi</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
from which it differs externally in the forewing pattern: 
<taxonomicName id="36AC4D05970BE363F000FB2E07A403E6" baseAuthorityName="Druce" baseAuthorityYear="1897" box="[355,490,1204,1228]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Episcepsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="moloneyi">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F000FB2E07A403E6" box="[355,490,1204,1228]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">E. moloneyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
does not have the veins well marked in a darker hue of brown as it happens in 
<taxonomicName id="36AC4D05970BE363F4E7FB2E071C03DA" authorityName="Pinheiro &amp; Araujo Junior" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="Pinheiro &amp; Araujo Junior" baseAuthorityYear="2017" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Episcepsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coeruleocephala" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F4E7FB2E071C03DA" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">E. coeruleocephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="D8EB57EF970BE363F000FB4C07A003DA" box="[355,494,1239,1264]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F000FB4C07A003DA" bold="true" box="[355,494,1239,1264]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">comb. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
On the other hand, the proximal area of hindwings is less marked in 
<taxonomicName id="36AC4D05970BE363F4E7FB42071C023E" authorityName="Pinheiro &amp; Araujo Junior" authorityYear="2017" baseAuthorityName="Pinheiro &amp; Araujo Junior" baseAuthorityYear="2017" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Episcepsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coeruleocephala" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F4E7FB42071C023E" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">E. coeruleocephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="D8EB57EF970BE363F03BFB670797023F" box="[344,473,1276,1301]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">
<emphasis id="C3D8EA94970BE363F03BFB670797023F" bold="true" box="[344,473,1276,1301]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">comb. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
